<body id = "homepagebackground">
	<div id = "homediv" style = "width:100%; min-width: 800px; margin:auto;">  
		<h1 style = "text-shadow: 1px 3px 3px #000000;color: #EEE;font-size: 240%;"> Interact with customers in your store. Online. </h1>
			<div  class = "hero-unit" style = "position: absolute;left:10%; width:600px; background-color: rgba(5,5,5,0.7); padding: 10px;">
				<h1 style = "color:#eee; font-size: 200%;">Butucu is a platform for brick-and-mortar stores to connect with in-store customers.</h1>
				<p style = "color: #bbb; padding:20px;">
					At Butucu, we're focused on bringing brick-and-mortar stores into the 21st century. Our solutions make it easy for <b>businesses and customers to engage</b> with one another, <b>sharing relevant information and feedback</b>.
				</p>
			</div>
				
			<div style = "position: absolute;left:50%;">
				<%= image_tag("combined.png", :height => '550', :width => '550')%>
			</div>
			
	</div>
	

	<div class="row center" style = "padding-top:20px; width:1100px"> 
	  <div class="well span4 " style = "height:220px;">
	    <h3><%= image_tag("signal.png", :height => '50', :width => '50', :class => "under") %> Push your content </h3>
	    <p> Businesses can customize content from real-time coupons to simple surveys to <b>communicate easily with customers</b>.
	    	Use our real-time chat to answer and interact with customers immediately.	    
	    </p>
	  </div>
	  <div class="well span4" style = "height:220px;float:left;">
	    <h3><%= image_tag("chat_logo.png", :height => '50', :width => '50', :class => "under") %> Customers love it</h3>
	    <p>
	    	Customers can engage with your store and get the information they need - <b>quickly</b> and <b>intuitively</b>. Customers can get the <b>convenience of an in-store app</b> without having to download a new app for each business.  
	    </p>	    
	  </div>
	  <div class="well span4" style = "height:220px;">
	    <h3><%= image_tag("analytics.png", :height => '50', :width => '50', :class => "under") %> Analytics </h3>
	    <p> We all know data's important. Our data will help you <b>understand your customers and address their needs</b>. Additionally, we're one of the first services to provide <b>comparative analytics</b> on customers between stores.
	    </p>	    
	  </div>
	  
	</div>
	<div id = "learn-more" style = "width:100%; min-width: 800px; margin:auto; padding:10px;"> 
	  <h1 style = "text-shadow: 1px 3px 3px #000000;color: #EEE;font-size: 240%;"> How It Works. </h1>
	  <div class="row center" style = "padding-top:20px; width:1500px"> 
		  <div class="well span4 " style = "height:300px;">
		    <h3>1. Businesses set up a 5 minute profile on Butucu</h3>
		    <p>
		    	Within 5 minutes, businesses can be up and running on Butucu:
	    	
	    		<li><b>0:00 - 2:00 </b> Enter your business name and address to get started </li>
	    		<li><b>2:00 - 3:00 </b> Confirm your account via email and our enterprise-level security</li>
	    		<li><b>3:00 - 5:00 </b> Create your first surveys and coupons, and view a dashboard of your store</li>
	    	
		    </p>
		  </div><div class="well span4 " style = "height:300px;">
		    <h3>2. Businesses create custom content</h3>
		    <p>
		    	Butucu currently lets businesses create custom <b>coupons</b> and <b>surveys</b>, as well as a <b>live chat</b> and help desk.	    
		    </p>
		    <p>
		    	<li><b>Coupons</b> can be created or destroyed instantly to manage inventory. </li>
	    		<li><b>Surveys</b> can let businesses measure <em>net promoter score</em> or A/B test product ideas. </li>
    			<li><b>Live chat</b> can resolve and track problems with customers to ensure a positive shopping experience. </li>
		    </p>
		  </div><div class="well span4 " style = "height:300px;">
		    <h3>3. Customers access and interact with content</h3>
		    <p>
		    	When customers visit www.butucu.com, they are <b>automatically routed</b> to the relevant store based on their location - quick and seamless.    
		    </p>
		    <p>
		    	Here, customers already inside the store can <b>engage with the businesses</b>, viewing point of sale coupons in exchange for feedback and surveys.
		    </p>
		  </div>
		  <div class="well span4 " style = "height:300px;">
		    <h3>4. Businesses gain insightful analytics</h3>
		    <p>
		    	For each <b>anonymized customer</b> that enters your store, Butucu can measure time spent in store, engagement with coupons and surveys, use of live chat and sentiment analysis of customer emotion.    
		    </p>
		    <p>
		    	Furthermore, view the <b>profiles of your customers</b> in terms of what other businesses they visit. Identify <b>high-value and high-risk repeat customers</b>.
		    </p>
		  </div>
		  
		  
		</div>
	</div>
